<item>
            <title>[OWB-354] WebContextService may throw NPE in tiered classloading environmemt</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OWB-354</link>
                <project id="12310844" key="OWB">OpenWebBeans</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;WebContextService sets the static context variables (which are ThreadLocals) to null during a call to destroy.  For example requestContext.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In a classloading environment where the same WebContextService would be shared between webapps, this could lead to a NullPointerException in another application as the static variable has been set to null and that static would be shared.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
